I thought of Lassie until the morning came...

18
00:03:33,890 --> 00:03:35,750
It is the result of the geological survey.

19
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:38,660
If the result is zero,
I can't assume that!

20
00:03:38,791 --> 00:03:39,431
Yes!

21
00:03:39,705 --> 00:03:42,595
Let's do our best and find coal, Dad!

22
00:03:43,634 --> 00:03:49,838
When I see these two working, I feel
that the coal will definitely come out!

23
00:03:50,252 --> 00:03:50,947
Yes!

24
00:03:51,170 --> 00:03:54,210
Well, we too will not lose
to the current manager!

25
00:03:54,337 --> 00:03:55,447
Yeah!

26
