There is no escape from that as you see...

30
00:04:13,377 --> 00:04:15,041
What are you saying?

31
00:04:15,166 --> 00:04:16,439
This is your gift!

32
00:04:16,658 --> 00:04:17,299
Oh?

33
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:19,549
Thank you...

34
00:04:20,530 --> 00:04:23,353
I... why I'm always so?

35
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:26,197
And to get sick at such an important time?

36
00:04:26,580 --> 00:04:28,080
I feel embarrassed by myself.

37
00:04:28,230 --> 00:04:30,416
I can't help John at all.

38
00:04:30,642 --> 00:04:31,610
Maybe so!

39
00:04:31,713 --> 00:04:33,916
So the same with me!

40
00:04:34,330 --> 00:04:39,752
All I can do is make tea at their own leisure!

41
00:04:40,057 --> 00:04:40,791
Yes...

42
00:04:41,030 --> 00:04:45,978
John is doing hard work like a man.

43
00:04:46,283 --> 00:04:46,940
Ah...!

44
00:04:47,002 --> 00:04:52,103
But when everyone treats the candy they offer
them will increase their strength as I think!

45
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,634
Thank you!

46
00:04:54,778 --> 00:04:55,744
John...

47
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:59,368
Actually wants to find Lassie but he can't!

48
00:04:59,705 --> 00:05:03,752
That's why he desperately tries
to find coal with others.

49
00:05:04,460 --> 00:05:07,994
When Lassie returns,
they will always live together.

50
00:05:09,432 --> 00:05:10,307
Hm...

51
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:15,877
I hope Lassie returns while he is in this area.

52
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:21,460
When I see it in good health,
I expect to stay next to it.

53
00:05:21,901 --> 00:05:22,752
Hm...

54
00:05:22,970 --> 00:05:25,541
I wish I could do even a little!

55
00:05:26,049 --> 00:05:26,791
Ah...

56
00:05:26,890 --> 00:05:28,236
You can't...

57
00:05:33,890 --> 00:05:35,415
And now everyone!

58
00:05:35,549 --> 00:05:37,103
Time for tea!

59
00:05:37,369 --> 00:05:39,479
