60
00:05:39,690 --> 00:05:42,310
The meat pie is full of energy!

61
00:05:42,478 --> 00:05:45,455
Every day I look forward to this moment!

62
00:05:45,549 --> 00:05:46,869
Well, take a break!

63
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:58,775
What do you think?

64
00:05:59,387 --> 00:06:01,259
