Yes?

68
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,815
I don't help much!

69
00:06:18,890 --> 00:06:20,425
Don't help too much?

70
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,784
You do everything you can!

71
00:06:23,636 --> 00:06:24,370
Hm?

72
00:06:25,698 --> 00:06:26,878
<i>What is that?</i>

73
00:06:27,671 --> 00:06:29,284
Ah, one week only?

74
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,206
Yes.

75
00:06:30,587 --> 00:06:31,945
It is time to hold your breath!

76
