Wellington Coal Mine has reached its limit.

77
00:06:34,557 --> 00:06:38,096
The bank is no longer able
to pay costs without interest!

78
00:06:39,002 --> 00:06:41,210
Now we can't extract coal.

79
00:06:41,362 --> 00:06:42,900
Maybe we should give up.

80
00:06:42,994 --> 00:06:45,000
But, just a week!

81
00:06:45,089 --> 00:06:45,917
Sam...

82
00:06:46,604 --> 00:06:49,963
I have to tell everyone the truth!

83
00:06:50,338 --> 00:06:53,291
<i>We need to think about
the future of our new life!</i>

84
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:58,705
We should talk to John.

85
00:07:00,385 --> 00:07:02,580
Do you have the power to tell him directly?

86
00:07:03,385 --> 00:07:05,487
